  {
    "name": "Great Engineer",
    "unitType": "Civilian",
    "uniques": [
         "Comment [-Architects, engineers, and master builders entrusted with turning ambitious plans into expensive realities.\nThey raise monuments, fortifications, and wonders that rulers proudly claim as their own achievements.\nEvery great structure stands as a testament to genius, organization, and someone else's back pain.\n• Great Person]",
