    "unitType": "Civilian",
    "uniques": [
         "Comment [-Prophets claim to speak for the gods. Their followers tend to agree.\nThey spread faith, settle theological disputes, and occasionally start entirely new ones.\nA wise prophet can unite a people under a common creed. An unwise one can still achieve the same result through fear and confusion.\n• Great Person\n• Religious Unit]",
